casebody.data:
Fourth Department,

February, 2009

(February 6, 2009) The People of the State of New York ex rel. Anthony Jackson, Appellant, v Harold Graham, Superintendent, Auburn Correctional Facility, Respondent. [872 NYS2d 687]

Appeal from a judgment (denominated order) of the Supreme Court, Cayuga County (Thomas G. Leone, A.J.), entered November 29, 2007 in a habeas corpus proceeding. The judgment denied the petition.

It is hereby ordered that the judgment so appealed from is unanimously affirmed without costs. Present—Scudder, P.J., Hurlbutt, Centra, Green and Gorski, JJ.
